        jTextArea1.setText("Thank you for choosing to use 'Dev Timer' \n\nThis program was written as a non commercial project to help improve my Java prgoramming skills, it theirfor comes with no warantee of functionality, but on the other hand can be freely distributed and legally used without any form of payment.\n\nThe intention of this program is to create a simple and reliable film developing timer, allowing the end user to input their desired default times for various parts of the developing process (e.g. default pre wash, stop bath, fixer, hypo clearing, final wash & wetting agent times), options are also offered to store a desired default agitation regime.\n\nTo allow you, the end user to develop your films whilst watching a film I have also integrated audible indicators as reminders of agitation and chemistry change.");
