        jTextArea2.setText("To modify the default settings select 'Set default options' from the menu, or alternatively press 'ALT + D'.\n\nIn the 'Set default options' panel you can change the default  times for:\n\nPre wash\nDeveloper\nStop bath\nFixer\nHypo clearing\nFinal wash\nWetting agent\n\nOptions are also available to set the default agitation settings:\n\nInitial agitation: - The initial agitation defines the amount of time to perform agitation from the start of each chemical process.\n\nThen X seconds/minute: - This option allows you to set a reccuring agitation that is repeated every minute of the developing process,");
